### 3.1 Core Principle
We sell belonging, safety, and status — not ads. Every monetization stream must satisfy one of three deep human needs:
- **Safety & Certainty** (I need to know what’s happening, I need to protect my family/community)
- **Belonging & Identity** (I want to be part of something meaningful, a movement)
